00:03:20.075 --> 00:03:21.451
<font color="#fecb00">What were you doing?</font>

3
00:03:21.869 --> 00:03:22.952
<font color="#fecb00">In Alaska.</font>

4
00:03:22.953 --> 00:03:24.162
<font color="#fecb00">out in the desert...</font>

5
00:03:24.872 --> 00:03:26.498
<font color="#fecb00">Did you know Godzilla was there?</font>

6
00:03:27.291 --> 00:03:29.542
<font color="#fecb00">I didn't know it would be Godzilla.</font>

7
00:03:29.543 --> 00:03:31.503
<font color="#fecb00">but I needed to draw out a Titan.</font>

8
00:03:32.588 --> 00:03:33.588
<font color="#fecb00">Why?</font>

9
00:03:34.423 --> 00:03:35.757
<font color="#fecb00">To open a rift.</font>

10
00:03:36.842 --> 00:03:38.635
<font color="#fecb00">To prove the network exists.</font>

11
00:03:43.348 --> 00:03:44.641
<font color="#fecb00">There's a gateway</font>

12
00:03:45.517 --> 00:03:46.643
<font color="#fecb00">that leads to their world</font>

13
00:03:47.436 --> 00:03:49.479
<font color="#fecb00">inside our own.</font>

14
00:03:50.355 --> 00:03:52.107
<font color="#fecb00">All this to prove your theory was right?</font>

15
00:03:54.484 --> 00:03:57.237
<font color="#fecb00">That my parents were right.</font>

16
00:03:58.030 --> 00:04:01.283
<font color="#fecb00">If they hadn't been dismissed as
lunatics. heretics. by Monarch...</font>

17
00:04:02.201 --> 00:04:03.827
<font color="#fecb00">maybe G-Day would never have happened.</font>

18
00:04:09.541 --> 00:04:10.667
<font color="#fecb00">Maybe Cate</font>

19
00:04:11.376 --> 00:04:12.711
<font color="#fecb00">would still be here.</font>

20
00:04:16.714 --> 00:04:18.841
<font color="#fecb00">Cate's not dead because of Monarch.</font>

21
00:04:20.636 --> 00:04:21.762
<font color="#fecb00">She's dead because of us.</font>

22
00:04:23.263 --> 00:04:25.057
<font color="#fecb00">Because I believed in you.</font>

23
00:04:27.100 --> 00:04:28.620
<font color="#fecb00">But all you ever cared about was this!</font>

24
00:04:34.274 --> 00:04:35.274
<font color="#fecb00">That isn't true.</font>

25
00:04:38.237 --> 00:04:39.797
<font color="#fecb00">I only wanted to protect you from this.</font>

26
00:04:41.657 --> 00:04:44.076
<font color="#fecb00">But you didn't need my protection.</font>

27
00:04:47.412 --> 00:04:48.914
<font color="#fecb00">That was my mistake.</font>

28
00:04:56.630 --> 00:05:00.050
<font color="#fecb00">You want to spare others the pain we feel?</font>

29
00:05:02.344 --> 00:05:05.639
<font color="#fecb00">You want to find a way for the
human species to survive?</font>

30
00:05:08.100 --> 00:05:09.226
<font color="#fecb00">Help me.</font>

31
00:05:09.434 --> 00:05:10.853
<font color="#fecb00">Work with me.</font>

32
00:05:11.144 --> 00:05:12.353
<font color="#fecb00">We can solve this.</font>

33
00:05:12.354 --> 00:05:13.354
<font color="#fecb00">Together.</font>

34
00:05:14.439 --> 00:05:15.607
<font color="#fecb00">Solve what?</font>

35
00:05:15.816 --> 00:05:17.442
<font color="#fecb00">The secret of co-existence.</font>

36
00:05:23.407 --> 00:05:24.407
<font color="#fecb00">All right.</font>

37
00:05:27.369 --> 00:05:28.954
<font color="#fecb00">If you can answer one question.</font>

38
00:05:33.292 --> 00:05:34.918
<font color="#fecb00">That's what matters to you now?</font>

39
00:05:36.545 --> 00:05:38.630
<font color="#fecb00">With the fate of the world at stake?</font>

40
00:05:42.593 --> 00:05:44.469
<font color="#fecb00">The choice I made...</font>

41
00:05:46.054 --> 00:05:49.266
<font color="#fecb00">You think I haven't tried
to understand it myself?</font>

42
00:05:52.561 --> 00:05:55.897
<font color="#fecb00">Would you rather that I hadn't
fallen in love with your mother?</font>

43
00:05:55.898 --> 00:05:58.357
<font color="#fecb00">That our family never existed?</font>

44
00:05:58.358 --> 00:06:00.235
<font color="#fecb00">Our family doesn't exist.</font>

45
00:06:02.154 --> 00:06:03.322
<font color="#fecb00">Not anymore.</font>

46
00:16:07.718 --> 00:16:09.636
<font color="#fecb00">I told you it wouldn't take long.</font>

47
00:16:13.223 --> 00:16:16.101
<font color="#fecb00">I gave most everything away.</font>

48
00:16:19.605 --> 00:16:21.648
<font color="#fecb00">I still need to make a few more trips.</font>

49
00:16:23.734 --> 00:16:25.110
<font color="#fecb00">Where will you go?</font>

50
00:16:28.322 --> 00:16:29.573
<font color="#fecb00">San Francisco.</font>

51
00:16:31.783 --> 00:16:33.952
<font color="#fecb00">Just for a few days.</font>

52
00:16:34.953 --> 00:16:37.788
<font color="#fecb00">There are some things I need to do...</font>

53
00:16:37.789 --> 00:16:39.374
<font color="#fecb00">for the divorce.</font>

54
00:16:45.255 --> 00:16:46.297
<font color="#fecb00">Emiko.</font>

55
00:16:46.298 --> 00:16:48.800
<font color="#fecb00">from now on...</font>

56
00:16:52.763 --> 00:16:55.640
<font color="#fecb00">After the attack on San Francisco.</font>

57
00:16:55.641 --> 00:16:57.934
<font color="#fecb00">we called everyone we could think of.</font>

58
00:16:57.935 --> 00:17:00.520
<font color="#fecb00">Hospitals. The Red Cross.</font>

59
00:17:00.521 --> 00:17:02.813
<font color="#fecb00">We searched the internet.</font>

60
00:17:02.814 --> 00:17:06.401
<font color="#fecb00">I never gave up hope that
you would come home.</font>

61
00:17:15.868 --> 00:17:18.121
<font color="#fecb00">We dreamed about this day.</font>

62
00:17:27.256 --> 00:17:30.341
<font color="#fecb00">No matter what you did to me.</font>

63
00:17:30.342 --> 00:17:34.596
<font color="#fecb00">your son deserves a
relationship with his father.</font>

64
00:17:44.106 --> 00:17:45.816
<font color="#fecb00">So please.</font>

65
00:17:47.401 --> 00:17:49.361
<font color="#fecb00">when you find out where you'll be staying.</font>

66
00:17:50.529 --> 00:17:52.281
<font color="#fecb00">let Kentaro know.</font>

67
00:25:42.459 --> 00:25:43.961
<font color="#fecb00">I thought you wanted my help?</font>

68
00:27:01.413 --> 00:27:03.133
<font color="#fecb00">You sound like you don't
want it to be true.</font>

69
00:27:03.415 --> 00:27:05.042
<font color="#fecb00">Of course I want it to be true!</font>

70
00:27:05.501 --> 00:27:08.461
<font color="#fecb00">But there's a big difference between
what you want to be and what could be.</font>

71
00:41:13.932 --> 00:41:15.142
<font color="#fecb00">You got so big.</font>

72
00:41:31.950 --> 00:41:33.452
<font color="#fecb00">I'm so sorry.</font>

73
00:41:36.163 --> 00:41:37.581
<font color="#fecb00">I'm so sorry.</font>

